# SimpleX Chat Integration

When working with SimpleX Chat in this project, consult **[docs/SIMPLEX_CHAT_REFERENCES.md](docs/SIMPLEX_CHAT_REFERENCES.md)** for:

- Package usage (`simplex-chat`, `@simplex-chat/types`)
- Official docs, CLI, and API links
- Debugging checklist and event types
- Project-specific patterns (trigger events, send API, credentials)

## Key Points

- Use `ChatClient` from `simplex-chat` for WebSocket/API; `@simplex-chat/types` for `T.ChatInfo`, `T.ChatItem`, `T.CIFile`, `T.ChatType`, `ChatResponse`
- WebSocket/CLI JSON protocol is not fully documented; rely on the TypeScript client and types
- Trigger events: `newChatItems`, `contactConnected`, `rcvFileComplete`, `rcvFileAccepted`
- Send messages: `chat.apiSendTextMessage(T.ChatType.Direct, contactId, message)`
- Credentials: see `credentials/SimplexityApi.credentials.ts`
